{"tid":1533843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主法案近了 林鄭應當悔改","createTime":"2019-09-02T23:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T00:02:01.000Z","uid":6940,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1337f7e88bd5098cc6695470bedc39b9751db308","tid":1533843,"uid":6940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T23:49:42.000Z","msg":"理性分析下，會唔會仲有幾日開國會<br />\n咁岩就流出林鄭段錄音<br />\n<br />\n我當d內容都係真，亦唔係佢自己放料<br />\n咁又會唔會可以同商界講到咁多接近唔出得街既內容<br />\n<br />\n你要唔俾公眾先，就唔會公開講 <br />\n即係話：講得就預左人知<br />\n<br />\n而家仲要講到推完例後悔喇：辭唔到職就咩都唔關自己事 你地有咩就上去問阿爺 <br />\n<br />\n大家唔好忘記！邊個7.1擺空城計，然後中聯辦再擺一次空城計，正式老屈顏色革命、拉支那落水 。<br />\n<br />\n再推一步黎講，我地行岩左，唔好放棄，一定要制裁到班狗官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5165c0adb6fb4f010768517dd4603e5bba89c6de","tid":1533843,"uid":52763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T23:50:29.000Z","msg":"聽講制裁名單水蛇春咁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b701ea29e6b37e495f7d00aef98c21abb497a7de","tid":1533843,"uid":266569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T23:55:19.000Z","msg":"我正式宣布香港人要6大訴求, 要加埋解散現役警隊及重組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533820</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"29d9392ea739e55baa700ef064575ac07acc213a","tid":1533843,"uid":9049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T23:59:16.000Z","msg":"主呀<br />\n<br />\n求你賜示威者有智慧面對向種難關<br />\n<br />\n奉主名求<br />\n<br />\n阿們"},{"pid":"83c6da5933bc871c9e448f48b8ca687dfa85f3a0","tid":1533843,"uid":98731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:00:47.000Z","msg":"【美國巴絲】請聯絡你嘅地區同州嘅國會代表／議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531469\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531469</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0a79429a0f8f31390ac188ad397ca79bc3e2a55f","tid":1533843,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00: